{"tid":457314,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人想關愛下我空虛寂寞凍既前度?","createTime":"2017-11-03T17:29:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T18:01:57.000Z","uid":37713,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4dc09f3ff73bb2e1d7dc9df8bf187428565b9d94","tid":457314,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T17:29:26.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n同前度分左手差不多兩年半了<br />\n分左手無耐我就因為佢太煩太chur所以block晒佢啲野<br />\n包括wtsapp fb ig<br />\n但係呢位人兄唔知係咪真係太寂寞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咁打千字文比我睇想求我回心轉意返去比佢撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最初呢佢都幾有道義，特登拎返以前個mk qooza出黎日日寫日記叫春<br />\n同我講：如果你仲在意既就開黎睇下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但唔知係咪因為佢後來知道我根本wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以之後每次叫春，<br />\n都會直接用sms sd過黎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n監生迫我睇<br />\n<br />\n其實佢以前都係5p台常客黎架，<br />\n成日係啲樹窿post到見到佢既<br />\n又成日有意無意咩post都留啲關於個ex<br />\n即係我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 既內容<br />\n例如人地話一人一隻忘記唔到既olg<br />\n佢就講 xxx，如果唔係唔會識到(我)，唔會成長 咁話喎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我覺得佢要叫春就一定有位(而且仲好多添)<br />\n但係佢又成日sd sms過黎震鳩我部電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗佢應該真係空虛寂寞凍想搵個人傾下計呀<br />\n前排仲見到佢係交配post留左tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴絲好心幫下佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係喎 同佢講野可能要用書面語喎，<br />\n因為佢啱啱講自己飲左罐狗也不屌既藍冰都講得好斯文。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/w5srp8dz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fw5srp8dz&h=e60fa199&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1000e3c7942a03d0c97fdf60f3b49c5704acb4d2","tid":457314,"u