img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪啦"},{"pid":"146c07516275353536b51cc132d0eccd1e7e0fa6","tid":457314,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T17:52:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果我冇get錯 你果陣好癲下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我而家都好癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比佢搞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n散左唔好理啦 唔係真係無彎轉</blockquote><br />\n佢迫我理，佢夾硬sd晒落我部手機到叫我睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nwtsapp fb ig tg乜乜柒柒都封晒啦我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似有得mute/block</blockquote><br />\n咁點解係要我mute唔係佢自己收聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做好心幫佢搵下人同佢傾計，唔好再煩住我了唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次一見到佢個名彈出黎都好想嘔"},{"pid":"c5573de4297f850ee97fd1ba056e18ff52dbf089","tid":457314,"uid":31911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T17:54:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咩名 可能見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪都想幫關愛下呢位咁可憐既男人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登真係有愛架<br />\nin mk濛 we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你之前究竟叫咩名🤔</blockquote><br />\n唔知你有無印象係舊登見過一個post係講有個變態佬入左前度fb unblock自己<br />\n仲迫佢前度睇佢千字文<br />\n個位前度就係我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講起上黎都嬲嬲地，<br />\n無人想睇你叫春呀。男人老狗日鳩日扮可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對舊登個post有啲印象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e4a3b03be249c53fa29f3279f531d812e038a1","tid":457314,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T17:54:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/015406_2710b59cee5b692a17932a2a0421ab56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F015406_2710b59cee5b692a17932a2a0421ab56.png&h=a6b6c9d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解自己講分手先仲可以拎出黎呃正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04e4a3ba4fa680a2a2d976df90ffd6433c566cc","tid":457314,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T17:55:52.000Z","msg":"呢啲人我唔出聲屌鳩佢真係會得寸進尺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已讀佢佢就當我默許<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9be4b2d9e623e41d330137d44b702adfd86041","tid":457314,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T17:57:10.000Z","msg":"咁我都信你真係俾佢煩到冇辦法先出黎講<br />\n男人死纏爛打到咁實在太肉酸"},{"pid":"ccbb17f0523ec3073c1f02346cb3bde063df524e","tid":457314,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T18:00:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">連登有愛</span><br />\n快啲黎關愛下佢<br />\n佢話自己有少少肌肉架，絲打們考慮下...同佢傾一兩句計啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a02f9787d0b0144f1e02f3a63336eedf97a5918","tid":457314,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T18:01:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">連登有愛</span><br />\n快啲黎關愛下佢<br />\n佢話自己有少少肌肉架，絲打們考慮下...同佢傾一兩句計啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8aeea0444b92a53c6151e25c61929bdd1b6b16","tid":457314,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T18:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/d5894hkf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fd5894hkf&h=dd7e6659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實你到底有無一次係守過承諾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a001d5a7962e6640b88d17dd3bf9bca8aa163ebb","tid":457314,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T18:04:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">連登有愛</span><br />\n快啲黎關愛下佢<br />\n佢話自己有少少肌肉架，絲打們考慮下...同佢傾一兩句計啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nin mk濛 we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>96巴 讀緊書放工番pt 覺得生活好機械式<br />\n志在搵到人吹水 男女冇所謂<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/kandayeung\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkandayeung&d=9OMDtgqKsXJWl5qPXZvpZ%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=531b6ebc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/kandayeung</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"93d83ab09a5c52ad72d51e9e510fd749764a4439","tid":457314,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T18:05:06.000Z","msg":"佢應該係唔介意你block<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後佢就可以一路send野俾你自high<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e90b1988913f75f81b9f7331300cecb1f0ac67","tid":457314,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T18:11:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢應該係唔介意你block<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後佢就可以一路send野俾你自high<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔似<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4dq7z36l\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4dq7z36l&h=49eeec6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b97231b1a4375c2fbb5764c72c75db6b1faca158","tid":457314,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T18:12:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢好脆弱呀，好需要多啲巴絲呵護佢既玻璃心"},{"pid":"54c7fe8d8b772f3d7a408d1831a219ad3155af41","tid":457314,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T18:24:04.000Z","msg":"成長? 邊撚到成長呀睇過?<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rmvs2abz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frmvs2abz&h=ccf34679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n扮暈扮入醫院但其實乜事都無<br />\n次次sd sms過黎又話頭痛又話食藥<br />\n由同我一齊個陣話介手介到廿歲人<br />\n其實分分鐘連紅筆都懶得畫一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人扮可憐你扮可憐，<br />\n人地港女起碼有個樣有個格，<br />\n你? 男人老狗扮乜春呀<br />\n成日話我少少錯都唔比機會你改<br />\n咁係邊個講分手呀???<br />\n扮受害者? 唔好再早啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"360e93730f138bb81a477a2b2bf6f069b26e8c2d","tid":457314,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T18:26:23.000Z","msg":"當初咩事分手呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349fd4c1e8b7cdc77db9cacc0bf9717ef4c88fdf","tid":457314,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T18:28:48.000Z","msg":"幾撚時都話人厚面皮就天下無敵，<br />\n我懶撚得理你諗住小事化無就變本加厲。<br />\n兩年前一直講叫你咪撚再搵我，一粒字都唔想睇，<br />\n睇親都想嘔，係，係停左兩三個月囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後又再黎過。<br />\n口講話想我拍拖想我幸福叫我快啲搵新男朋友，<br />\n事實就係每次見到你個名彈出黎粒玻璃心又再碎過。<br />\n其實你都幾識玩呀，想搏我30歲無人埋單由你黎埋單呀嘛，<br />\nsor9ly，孤獨終老都唔會再想見到你。"},{"pid":"4dcb31848badadc4374248155bc1ef6001122a47","tid":457314,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T18:30:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當初咩事分手呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\num 你係咪好想知<br />\n因為有少少長<br />\n唔係帽"},{"pid":"fe6f62fa67d3006e69ae86c79290ec4d21fd4d3d","tid":457314,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T18:32:04.000Z","msg":"一睇到呢d長文 對你d印象就返晒黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faedb42b48b98b35d1b3e205acfb8c7945b9382c","tid":457314,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T18:32:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當初咩事分手呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\num 你係咪好想知<br />\n因為有少少長<br />\n唔係帽</blockquote><br />\n講嚟聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45eb6f9cec243ce9335ef47f1d86c5e661e73ee","tid":457314,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T18:34:04.000Z","msg":"今次當面屌撚柒你，我知你一撚定見到。<br />\n你下次夠膽再sd一粒字過黎，一粒，<br />\n一點都計，<br />\n我即刻放你電話上黎叫巴絲提你屙夜尿，屌你老母。"},{"pid":"d10c738752767f41ebafdf0946ffe3901cbb8a17","tid":457314,"uid":5725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T18:38:32.000Z","msg":"屌. 睇左陣先發現係GAY POST"},{"pid":"4cb188c695816e7d906699ba460582413ce37ee6","tid":457314,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T18:44:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>當初咩事分手呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\num 你係咪好想知<br />\n因為有少少長<br />\n唔係帽</blockquote><br />\n講嚟聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本身同佢講好左十八歲可以扑野既，但要過左我生日先<br />\n個陣同佢都拍左四年幾架啦，有用手同口幫過佢既，<br />\n而家諗返都覺得自己污糟，屌<br />\n<br />\n咁我生日就係動漫展兩個月之後啦，個陣五月幾講起，<br />\n佢就話不如動漫個晚去開房啦，我就話唔好<br />\n佢係咁話去，我係咁話唔好，佢講左好多句既，個態度都唔似講笑既<br />\n講到我嬲，我就咩粗口都出晒叫佢收聲，但佢唔肯<br />\n到後尾我頂唔順叫佢咪撚搵我，佢仲話鳩我小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁就冷戰左成兩個禮拜<br />\n<br />\n兩個禮拜後佢有試圖問返我出唔出街，但我個時仲未嬲完既，<br />\n搵啲咁既野黎玩，屌你老母<br />\n後尾都無疾而終，無幾耐佢就同我講分手<br />\n佢話我一嬲就唔理佢，覺得自己好似一隻狗，<br />\n個晚我有嘗試去箍煲，我話我可以改，但佢話好攰，<br />\n第二日仲鬧我話四年幾無為佢付出過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比佢咁樣講一講，個下我都攰，就大家都講左分手<br />\n<br />\n點知過左兩個月返黎搵我復合，話咩無左我唔得，<br />\n話個時講既全部都係籍口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢越黎越chur，我越黎越反感，之後就block左了<br />\n基本上係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實好on9"},{"pid":"f44439824df351757a04082f9aa5df011bb78a2b","tid":457314,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T18:45:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌. 睇左陣先發現係GAY POST</blockquote><br />\n佢話男女都傾得架，巴打快啲幫下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}